<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Pwsh on CornRadio-Blog</title><link>https://b.cornradio.org/tags/pwsh/</link><description>Recent content in Pwsh on CornRadio-Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 19 Sep 2023 09:32:55 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://b.cornradio.org/tags/pwsh/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>powershell 设置别名 alias</title><link>https://b.cornradio.org/p/powershell-%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%88%AB%E5%90%8D-alias/</link><pubDate>Tue, 19 Sep 2023 09:32:55 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://b.cornradio.org/p/powershell-%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%88%AB%E5%90%8D-alias/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://b.cornradio.org/pwsh.jpg" alt="Featured image of post powershell 设置别名 alias" />&lt;p>使用 zsh 之后，回到windows，我很怀念alias功能。 以及 zshrc 配置文件。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>但是 powershell 可以实现类似的功能：&lt;a class="link" href="https://blog.csdn.net/lei_qi/article/details/106592404" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>参考&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>打开管理员 powershell ， 执行允许ps1脚本的命令：&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ol start="2">
&lt;li>编辑配置文件（可以用任何自己喜欢的编辑器）&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-pwsh" data-lang="pwsh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">code&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">$PROFILE&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-powershell" data-lang="powershell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c"># 例如：&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c"># 快速移动到 hugo 工作目录：&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">function&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">hg&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nb">Set-Location&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">-Path&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;C:\Users\kasus\hugo-win&amp;#39;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c"># 执行多行命令&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">function&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">xxx&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nb">Set-Location&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">-Path&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;C:\github\xxx&amp;#39;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">git&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">pull&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>